name: NervBox
summary:
Your Physics Playground Awaits
In NervBox, physics is the foundation. Every player is physically simulated, giving you the ability to get into chaotic close-quarters fights or cooperate to muscle around oversized contraptions. Build elaborate creations, collapse them in spectacular fashion, or invent entirely new games just by experimenting with the world. From futuristic sports to chaotic chain reactions, NervBox gives you the world for imagination and physics to...
